"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?18/51/19253/abstract/4\">",
"      Marks RD, Richter JE, Rizzo J, et al. Omeprazole versus H2-receptor antagonists in treating patients with peptic stricture and esophagitis. Gastroenterology 1994; 106:907.",
"     </a>",
